data.description: This all brick home has an open floor plan with vaulted kitchen-living room. Granite counters throughout with custom cabinetry. French doors open to a large covered back porch. Master suite has whirlpool tub with tiled shower and walk-in closet. Oversized garage with room for a workbench and lots of attic storage.
